title: Carlos Mencia: Not for the Easily Offended(2005)DVDRip.AC3(ENG)-
description:
Carlos Mencia built a name for himself as a Hispanic comic who was unafraid to tackle inflammatory racial and topical issues in his pointed monologues. Not for the Easily Offended -- Live in San Jose captures the performer doing what he does best, offering a series of humorous yet serious observations about the many ways different cultures fail to connect with each other. 

Ripped with Handbrake.
